{"tid":2260481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無神論者的巴別塔:為保關鍵一席放棄拉布","createTime":"2020-10-27T14:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T14:58:14.000Z","uid":53566,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"66557bce920fa86b5534a1ccb1f3776421f93e04","tid":2260481,"uid":53566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhenryporterbabel&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=7f1f1933\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/henryporterbabel</a><br />\n<br />\n大口狗呢招真係夠絕，先同班飯民講：「拿你如果驚許志峰保唔住個位比人DQ呢，最好就唔好拉<br />\n咁多布搞到飯民建制關係惡劣，聽聽話話個譴責動議咪唔會咁多建制派投贊成票囉」<br />\n然後轉個頭發展事務委員會副主席選舉，飯民立刻全體缺席，劉國勳順利當選──你睇飯民建制，幾有默契呀！<br />\n#為保關鍵一席放棄拉布<br />\n#本末倒置<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}